derivation: from H410 (אֵל) and H5828 (עֵזֶר); God of help;
outline:
Eliezer = "God is help"
  1. Abraham's Damascene servant
  2. a son of Moses
  3. a Benjamite
  4. a priest who helped move the ark
  5. a Reubenite
  6. a prophet who spoke to Jehoshaphat
  7. a Levite chief
  8. son of Harim
  9. priest with foreign wife
strongs_def: Eliezer, the name of a Damascene and of ten Israelites
